---
---

<section class="py-20 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto space-y-12">
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold">The Solution</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg">
        Write fragments. Compile to targets. Never resolve a semantic conflict again.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-8">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
        <div class="bg-gray-900 rounded-lg p-6 space-y-3">
          <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-400">1</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-white">Author Fragments</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">
            Write small Markdown files under <code class="bg-gray-800 px-1 py-0.5 rounded text-brand-300">agents/your-agent/</code>. One concern per file.
          </p>
          <pre class="bg-gray-800 text-gray-300 p-3 rounded text-xs overflow-x-auto"><code>agents/coder/
├── 010-role.md
├── 020-tools.md
└── 030-examples.md</code></pre>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-900 rounded-lg p-6 space-y-3">
          <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-400">2</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-white">Compile</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">
            Run <code class="bg-gray-800 px-1 py-0.5 rounded text-brand-300">agentquilt build</code> to generate deterministic Markdown targets.
          </p>
          <pre class="bg-gray-800 text-gray-300 p-3 rounded text-xs overflow-x-auto"><code>$ agentquilt build
✓ CLAUDE.md (3 blocks)
✓ AGENTS.md (5 blocks)</code></pre>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-900 rounded-lg p-6 space-y-3">
          <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-400">3</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-white">Enforce</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">
            <code class="bg-gray-800 px-1 py-0.5 rounded text-brand-300">agentquilt check</code> ensures targets are in sync with source.
          </p>
          <pre class="bg-gray-800 text-gray-300 p-3 rounded text-xs overflow-x-auto"><code>$ agentquilt check
✓ All targets up-to-date</code></pre>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-brand-900/30 border border-brand-800 rounded-lg p-6">
        <p class="text-gray-300">
          <span class="font-semibold text-brand-400">No more conflicts.</span> Each developer edits separate files. Git merges naturally. Diffs are readable.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
